@vera-liu needs this for her work so merging in now.
- shows text with copy link

usage:

```
<CopyToClipboard
  shouldShowText={true}
  text={html}
  copyNode={<i className="fa fa-clipboard" title="Copy to clipboard"></i>}
  onCopyEnd={() => { this.setState({ isCopied: true }); }}
/>
```

